Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纠正人类 夺回母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的使命...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神会在这次战争中利用你的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果战斗了 你的孩子也会死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不许欺负贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一点也没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还愿再陪我跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到圣女大人跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不是圣女了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔总在我陷入危机时赶到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去 我们与人类的关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 巴哈姆特引发灾难时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们同心协力 付出了巨大牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终保住了这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而人类失去了信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣称不再需要神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后袭击了我们的神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至犯下了弑神之举
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他们意识到自身的过错之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我们只能默默忍受此等暴行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不是决不能继续容忍人类的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让侮辱诸神的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好见识下我们的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为遇害的同胞雪耻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回世界的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加百列大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔的力量还是未知数
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知能否承受这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔能封印人类的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这己经证明过很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空艇队 上 上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步兵准备好投石车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把兵力集中到正面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧布置巨神兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利欧斯去死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王宫兵全去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要打仗就去外面打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了 再不逃就要开打了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争将考验我们的真正价值啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与神战斗 你就没任何感想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？那又如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 别跟凯撒团长说一样的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣战的可是神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后勤有劳你们咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才是前线的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类就在安全地方看戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们的王决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那态度是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄亚思 去干掉他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火开火开火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这拖着她们 你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑得很快的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续走 妮娜就找不到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什...什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来得是时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西继续跑下去能到哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你瞎跳啥舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那啥...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还愿再陪我跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 都抓稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我倒是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为要挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们在那干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:09:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那帮人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥在给我鼓劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护好陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂...神是不是太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个光芒能封印人类的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑兵部队在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付这种对手不是他们的拿手好戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连他们也受不了那光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就跑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告 城门被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就要杀入城中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个还未完成开发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在使用 不知陛下会出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没征求你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喊你拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们也差不多该动身了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒 把假手摘下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摘下来之后固定在锁上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先是伸出拇指 然后是中指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用问？当然是要逃出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着弯曲拇指 伸出食指和小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 尽可能离它远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（咒语）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你做个更好的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能用倒在那里的家伙的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这边的门也打开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你別把我另一只假手也炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不是我 是丽塔设置的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说什么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是都爆炸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:18:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么在这 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微变得女人些了吗 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德大人 平安无事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒 你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个 别磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你有锻炼自己的本事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是锻炼得杠杠的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.26,0:23:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招 看招看招
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神击的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告別武装
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:23:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射击之类的...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.89,0:23:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周记得看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.02,0:24:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂？
